Package: RwPFS
Title: Calculate and compare a range of real-world progression-free survival (rwPFS) endpoints.
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: c( 
    person(given = "Michael", family = "Bretscher", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "michael.bretscher@roche.com"),
    person("Shanmugasundaram", "Prabhu", email = "shanmup3@gene.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Nandi", "Kalyan", email = "nandik@gene.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Progression-free survival (PFS) is an important endpoint in clinical oncology trials. Multiple definitions of PFS are possible in real-world data (rwPFS). The RwPFS package provides tools to calculate and easily compare real-world PFS endpoints across a range of definitions.
BugReports: https://github.com/phcanalytics/RwPFS/issues
